Genre: Top Down Scrolling Shooter
Name: Drive 'N Shoot
  Help Mad Max traverse Fury Road. Mounted to the top and sides of your vehicle are machine guns and missile launchers to wipe
  out any potential threats along the way.
Goal: Destroy obstacles in the road with mounted weapons before they destroy you. Each section of the road is a new level.
Gameplay: Use the arrow keys to change lanes in the road and speed up over ramps. Use A, S, D, W to fire weapons.
How Levels Differ: As the levels advance, your vehicle speeds up and the enemies become stronger.

